LIGHTHOUSE TARGETS: Perf >= 95, A11y = 100, BP = 100, SEO >= 90
REQUIRED IN BUILT HTML:
- Landing copy in raw HTML source
- JSON-LD SoftwareApplication schema
- OG + Twitter meta tags with valid image asset
- Meta description under 155 chars with "energy-aware scheduling"
FONT: preload critical only, font-display:swap
IMAGES: explicit width+height, lazy below fold, modern formats
JS: route-split, defer non-critical, no render-blocking on landing
